snippet.title: Skycadia Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/skycadia-demo/9mvjdvq2vzcv
Sign up for updates on Skycadia, and learn more about the world: http://skycadia.com/
The world of Skycadia is overrun with sky pirates -- and there's profit to be made! Take to the skies and collect bounties by shooting down the scoundrels in this light-hearted flying adventure.

Featured in the Xbox One Summer Game Fest Demo Event, a special preview will be available for a limited time from July 21 to July 27! Download the Alpha demo today: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/skycadia-demo/9mvjdvq2vzcv

More info on the Summer Game Fest: https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2020/07/01/summer-game-fest-demo-event-xbox/
